<body>

<h1>@HI{{demo}}</h1>

<h2> Formation </h2>

<ol>
<li> @N{{}} <strong>@HI{{demo}}</strong>
</ol>

<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{demo}}</strong> means "even".

<ol>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KJ{{before^life}}<strong>demo</strong>machigaimashita.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Even a teacher makes mistakes.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{kokokara<strong>demo</strong>@KJ{{wealth^gentleman^mountain}}ga@KJ{{see}}iemasu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Even from here you can see Mount Fuji.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{ano@KJ{{person}}ha@KJ{{fish}}<strong>demo</strong>@KJ{{meat}}<strong>demo</strong>@KJ{{eat}}bemasu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      He eats both fish and meat.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</ol>
</p>

<h2> Notes </h2>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{demo}}</strong> is not the same as the combination of particles @HI{{de}} + @HI{{mo}}.
</p>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{demo}}</strong> combines with various WH-words.

<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{ano@KJ{{map^write^building}}hadare<strong>demo</strong>@KJ{{enter}}remasu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Anyone can enter that library.
  </td> </tr>
</table>

</p>

